  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Logistic Assistant",
  "description": "<p>Responsible of all outbound inventory stocks deliveries to Thomson Medical Centre as well as the Thomson Specialist clinics. Includes managing the goods return from wards, coordinate on any urgent/emergency item request from nursing wards/clinics/departments for after office hours deliveries as well as organizing stocks inventory items in warehouse.</p><p><strong>RESPONSIBILITIES</strong></p><p>·       Carry out daily logistics and warehouse operations, including receiving, issuing, and delivering goods.</p><p>·       Generate pick lists and pack items based on ward requisitions.</p><p>·       Perform quality and quantity inspections on goods received from vendors and suppliers.</p><p>·       Conduct regular inventory stock takes to ensure accurate records.</p><p>·       Monitor inventory expiry dates and ensure timely usage or disposal.</p><p>·       Prepare pick lists using the ERP Inventory system.</p><p>·       Deliver and collect patient case notes between wards and the Medical Records Office.</p><p>·       Coordinate the preparation and delivery of discharge marketing bags to Thomson Medical Centre.</p><p>·       Provide support in delivery of ad-hoc items for marketing events.</p><p>·       Organize warehouse storage space and housekeeping</p><p>·       Undertake any other duties as assigned by Warehouse Lead Supervisor / Department Head</p><p><strong>REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><p>·       ’O’ levels/NITEC</p><p>·       Min. 1 – 2 years of Logistics/Warehousing experience</p><p>·      Class 3 Driver License <br /></p><p><br />------</p><p>If you do not possess the above experience, your application will still be considered on individual merits and you may be contacted for other opportunities</p><p>By submitting your personal data and/or resume, you give consent to the collection, use and disclosure of your personal data and/or resume by the company (or its agent) for the purpose of the processing and administration by company relating to this job application.</p><p>**We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified.**</p>",
